      "description": "Get ready for a reliable companion that's seen some of the world and is ready for more! This vehicle is in fair condition, showing some honest character from its travels, but it remains a solid and practical choice for anyone seeking dependable transportation. It\u2019s a great opportunity to own a functional car at a price that respects your budget!",
