    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in drivable shape. The engine requires a complete rebuild as it suffered a major internal failure, and the transmission exhibits significant slipping when it was last operational. Externally, there is widespread rust on the rocker panels and wheel wells, along with several deep dents and heavily oxidized paint. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a cracked dashboard, and most of the electronic components, including the radio and power windows, are non-functional. This car is strictly a project for a dedicated mechanic or a valuable source of salvageable parts.",
