    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m so excited to pass this beauty along to a new home. It\u2019s been kept in absolutely incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks and feels just like it did the day it left the showroom! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s basically spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve gotta come check it out. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 42900.0,
