    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom state, having been strictly garage-kept and fastidiously maintained by a single enthusiast owner. The exterior retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster with zero stone chips or swirl marks, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium upholstery remains supple without a single crease or sign of wear, and all original appointments are intact. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive service portfolio documenting every scheduled maintenance interval. It drives with the tight, responsive precision of a car that just rolled off the assembly line. For the discerning buyer who demands perfection and a turn-key experience, this is an unparalleled opportunity.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
